#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/mail/_index.adoc:980
msgid ""
"The message index shows messages in the current directory and can be "
"navigated by using the cursor keys.  Highlighted messages can be read by "
"pressing kbd:[Enter]."
